snippet.title: Ragnarock - Official Sabaton Raid DLC Trailer | Upload VR Showcase 2023
snippet.description:
Get ready to lead your Viking brothers and sisters into victory with this new DLC pack for Ragnarok, including an entirely new environment to rock out in, as well as a new pair of hammers, a brand new longship, and six new tunes to bang out from Sabaton! The Sabaton Raid for Ragnarok will be available June, 22nd on Steam for PC, Meta Quest, PlayStation VR2, Viveport, and Pico.

#GameTrailers #VR #SummerofGaming
